name: INSTITUTE OF EDUCATION TRAINING AND DEVELOPMENT
briefDescription: IETD is the fulfillment of a dream by a few young individuals to help, co-operate and collaborate with others in the life journey so that life becomes easy. The idea of environmental protection and its preservation emerged from the firm belief that like us the next generations also needs this earth for sustaining life. To create a generation of technically skilled manpower emerged from the belief that nations economic prosperity lies in the hand of creative and contributing citizen.
